snippet.title: Fractal Sailor - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play for free on Win/Mac: https://propagant.itch.io/fractal-sailor

Fractal Sailor is an experimental, atmospheric horror tech demo where you take the role of a lone sailor navigating a hovercraft through a dark and mystic fractal environment.
However, you are not alone...
